{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we further investigated MAGs suspected of representing multiple subpopulations with a strain-haplotyping approach.",
    "In sample B, this uncovered a FQ resistance point mutation that was suppressed at the MAG level.",
    "In sample A, strain-level phylogenomic comparison related the metagenomic data to nearly identical isolates obtained from the same farm.",
    "However, many of the resulting phased assemblies in both samples remained incomplete or contaminated, or represented multiple strains.",
    "This was especially the case at low coverages, indicating insufficient strain separation."
  ]
}